extendedInfo.description: Urgent money-making business required! Who else wants to start a million dollar business? Owning a small business is everyone's dream and if it's not yours yet, it may become your priority, especially when you realize how easy it is to become unemployed. In today's world losing your job could become your reality, so it's smart to plan your own enterprise now, before anything happens.This app leads you through a step by step process.
